{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3000,"text":"For some time I have been interested in"},{"time":5000,"text":"the placebo effect,"},{"time":7000,"text":"which might seem like an odd thing"},{"time":9000,"text":"for a magician to be interested in,"},{"time":11000,"text":"unless you think of it in the terms that I do,"},{"time":13000,"text":"which is, \"Something fake"},{"time":17000,"text":"is believed in enough by somebody"},{"time":19000,"text":"that it becomes something real.\""},{"time":21000,"text":"In other words, sugar pills"},{"time":23000,"text":"have a measurable effect in certain kinds of studies,"},{"time":26000,"text":"the placebo effect,"},{"time":28000,"text":"just because the person thinks"},{"time":31000,"text":"that what's happening to them is a pharmaceutical"},{"time":33000,"text":"or some sort of a --"},{"time":36000,"text":"for pain management, for example,"},{"time":38000,"text":"if they believe it enough there is a measurable effect in the body"},{"time":40000,"text":"called the placebo effect."},{"time":42000,"text":"Something fake becomes"},{"time":44000,"text":"something real"},{"time":46000,"text":"because of someone's perception of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"In order for us to understand each other,"},{"time":51000,"text":"I want to start by showing you a rudimentary,"},{"time":53000,"text":"very simple magic trick."},{"time":55000,"text":"And I'm going to show you how it works. This is a trick"},{"time":57000,"text":"that's been in every children's magic book since at least the 1950s."},{"time":61000,"text":"I learned it myself from Cub Scout Magic in the 1970s."},{"time":65000,"text":"I'll do it for you, and then I'll explain it."},{"time":67000,"text":"And then I'll explain why I explained it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70000,"text":"So, here's what happens."},{"time":72000,"text":"The knife, which you can examine; my hand, which you could examine."},{"time":74000,"text":"I'm just going to hold the knife in my fist like this."},{"time":77000,"text":"I'll get my sleeve back."},{"time":79000,"text":"And to make sure nothing goes up or down my sleeve"},{"time":81000,"text":"I'm just going to squeeze my wrist right here."},{"time":84000,"text":"That way you can see that at no time"},{"time":86000,"text":"can anything travel, as long as I'm squeezing there"},{"time":88000,"text":"nothing can go up or down my sleeve."},{"time":91000,"text":"And the object of this is quite simple."},{"time":93000,"text":"I'm going to open my hand,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and hopefully, if all is well,"},{"time":99000,"text":"my pure animal magnetism will hold the knife."},{"time":102000,"text":"In fact it's held so tightly in place"},{"time":104000,"text":"that I can shake it,"},{"time":106000,"text":"and the knife does not come off."},{"time":109000,"text":"Nothing goes up or down my sleeve,"},{"time":111000,"text":"no trickery. And you can examine everything."},{"time":114000,"text":"Ta-da!"},{"time":116000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"So, this is a trick that I often teach to young children"},{"time":121000,"text":"that are interested in magic, because you can learn"},{"time":123000,"text":"a great deal about deception by studying"},{"time":125000,"text":"this very -- even though it's a very simple trick methodologically."},{"time":128000,"text":"Probably many of you in the room know this trick."},{"time":130000,"text":"What happens is this."},{"time":132000,"text":"I hold the knife in my hand."},{"time":134000,"text":"I say I'm going to grab hold of my wrist"},{"time":136000,"text":"to make sure nothing goes up or down my sleeve,"},{"time":138000,"text":"that is a lie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"The reason I'm holding onto my wrist"},{"time":142000,"text":"is because that's actually the secret"},{"time":144000,"text":"of the illusion."},{"time":146000,"text":"In a moment when my hand moves from facing you"},{"time":148000,"text":"to being away from you,"},{"time":150000,"text":"this finger right here, my index finger is just going to shift"},{"time":152000,"text":"from where it is, to a position"},{"time":155000,"text":"pointing out like this."},{"time":157000,"text":"Nice one."},{"time":159000,"text":"Someone who didn't have a childhood is out there."},{"time":162000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"So, it goes like this, from here, right."},{"time":166000,"text":"And as I move around my finger shifts."},{"time":168000,"text":"And we could talk about why this is deceptive,"},{"time":170000,"text":"why you don't notice there are only three fingers down here,"},{"time":173000,"text":"because the mind, and the way it processes information,"},{"time":175000,"text":"it doesn't count, one, two, three. It groups them."},{"time":178000,"text":"But that's not really what this is about. Right? And then I open my hand up."},{"time":180000,"text":"Obviously it's clinging there, not by animal magnetism,"},{"time":184000,"text":"but by chicanery,"},{"time":186000,"text":"my index finger being there."},{"time":189000,"text":"And then when I close my finger, same thing,"},{"time":191000,"text":"as I move back, this motion"},{"time":193000,"text":"kind of covers the moving back of my finger."},{"time":195000,"text":"I take this hand away. You give the knife out."},{"time":197000,"text":"There is a trick you can do for your friends and neighbors. Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"Now, (Laughter)"},{"time":203000,"text":"what does that have to do with the placebo effect?"},{"time":206000,"text":"I read a study a year or so ago"},{"time":209000,"text":"that really blew my mind wide open."},{"time":212000,"text":"I'm not a doctor or a researcher, so this, to me,"},{"time":214000,"text":"was an astonishing thing."},{"time":216000,"text":"It turns out that if you administer"},{"time":218000,"text":"a placebo in the form of a white pill,"},{"time":220000,"text":"that's like aspirin shaped --"},{"time":223000,"text":"it's just a round white pill -- it has some certain measurable effect."},{"time":226000,"text":"But if you change the form that you give the placebo in,"},{"time":229000,"text":"like you make a smaller pill,"},{"time":231000,"text":"and color it blue, and stamp a letter into it,"},{"time":234000,"text":"it is actually measurably more effective."},{"time":237000,"text":"Even though neither one of these things"},{"time":239000,"text":"has any pharmaceutical -- they're sugar pills."},{"time":242000,"text":"But a white pill is not as good as a blue pill."},{"time":246000,"text":"What? (Laughter) That really flipped me out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"Turns out though, that that's not even where it stops."},{"time":251000,"text":"If you have capsules,"},{"time":254000,"text":"they're more effective than tablets in any form."},{"time":256000,"text":"A colored capsule, that's yellow on one end and red on the other"},{"time":259000,"text":"is better than a white capsule."},{"time":261000,"text":"Dosage has something to do with this."},{"time":263000,"text":"One pill twice a day"},{"time":265000,"text":"is not as good at three pills --"},{"time":268000,"text":"I don't remember the statistic now. Sorry."},{"time":270000,"text":"But the point is ..."},{"time":272000,"text":"(Laughter) ... these dosages have something to do with it."},{"time":274000,"text":"And the form has something to do with it."},{"time":276000,"text":"And if you want the ultimate in placebo,"},{"time":279000,"text":"you've go to the needle."},{"time":282000,"text":"Right? A syringe with some inert --"},{"time":284000,"text":"a couple CCs of some inert something,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and you inject this into a patient ..."},{"time":288000,"text":"Well this is such a powerful image in their mind,"},{"time":290000,"text":"it's so much stronger than the white pill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"It's a really, this graph, well I'll show it to you"},{"time":295000,"text":"some other time when we have slides."},{"time":297000,"text":"The point is"},{"time":299000,"text":"the white pill is not as good as the blue pill"},{"time":302000,"text":"is not as good as the capsule is not as good as the needle."},{"time":305000,"text":"And none of it has any real pharmaceutical quality,"},{"time":308000,"text":"it's only your belief that makes it real"},{"time":312000,"text":"in your body and makes a stronger effect."},{"time":315000,"text":"I wanted to see if I could take that idea"},{"time":317000,"text":"and apply it to a magic trick."},{"time":319000,"text":"And take something that is obviously a fake trick"},{"time":323000,"text":"and make it seem real."},{"time":328000,"text":"And we know from that study"},{"time":331000,"text":"that when you want reality, you go to the needle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"This is a seven-inch hatpin. It's very, very sharp,"},{"time":339000,"text":"and I'm going to just sterilize it a tiny bit."},{"time":346000,"text":"This is really my flesh. This is not"},{"time":348000,"text":"Damian's special-grown flesh."},{"time":350000,"text":"That's my skin right there. This is not a Hollywood special effect."},{"time":355000,"text":"I'm going to pierce my skin"},{"time":357000,"text":"and run this needle through to the other side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"If you're queasy -- (Laughs)"},{"time":362000,"text":"if you faint easily -- I was doing this for some friends"},{"time":364000,"text":"in the hotel room last night, and some people that I didn't know,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and one woman almost passed out."},{"time":369000,"text":"So, I suggest if you get queasy easy"},{"time":372000,"text":"that you look away for about the next 30 --"},{"time":374000,"text":"in fact, you know what, I'll do the first bad part behind it."},{"time":376000,"text":"You'll get to see, you can look away too if you'd like to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"So, here is what happens, right here,"},{"time":382000,"text":"the beginning of my flesh"},{"time":384000,"text":"at the lower part of my arm I just make"},{"time":386000,"text":"a little pierce."},{"time":388000,"text":"I'm sorry, man. Am I freaking you out?"},{"time":390000,"text":"OK, and then just through my skin a tiny bit,"},{"time":394000,"text":"and then out the other side like this."},{"time":397000,"text":"Now, essentially we're in the same position we were in"},{"time":401000,"text":"with the knife trick."},{"time":403000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":407000,"text":"Sort of."},{"time":409000,"text":"But you can't count my fingers right now can you?"},{"time":412000,"text":"So, let me show them to you. That's one, two"},{"time":414000,"text":"three, four, five."},{"time":417000,"text":"Yes, well..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420000,"text":"I know what people think when they see this."},{"time":422000,"text":"They go, \"Well, he's certainly not dumb enough"},{"time":424000,"text":"to stab himself through the skin to entertain us for a few minutes."},{"time":427000,"text":"So, let me give you a little peek."},{"time":430000,"text":"How's that look out there? Pretty good."},{"time":432000,"text":"(Laughs)"},{"time":435000,"text":"Yeah, I know. (Laughs)"},{"time":438000,"text":"And the people in the back go, \"OK, I didn't really see that.\""},{"time":440000,"text":"People in the satellite room are starting to move in now."},{"time":443000,"text":"Let me give you good close look at this."},{"time":445000,"text":"That really is my skin. That is not a Hollywood special effect."},{"time":448000,"text":"That's my flesh, and I can twist that around."},{"time":451000,"text":"I'm sorry. If you're getting queasy, look away,"},{"time":453000,"text":"don't look at the thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455000,"text":"People in the back or people on video years from now watching this"},{"time":457000,"text":"will go, \"Well yeah, that looks kind of neat"},{"time":460000,"text":"in some sort of effect there, but if it were real he would be --"},{"time":463000,"text":"see there's a hole there and a hole there, if it were real he would be bleeding."},{"time":466000,"text":"Well let me work up some blood for you."},{"time":469000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":474000,"text":"Yes, there it is."},{"time":476000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":492000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"Normally now, I would take the needle out."},{"time":498000,"text":"I would clean off my arm, and I would show you that there are no wounds."},{"time":501000,"text":"But I think in this context"},{"time":504000,"text":"and with the idea of taking something fake"},{"time":506000,"text":"and making it into something real,"},{"time":509000,"text":"I'm just going to leave it there,"},{"time":511000,"text":"and walk off the stage."},{"time":513000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":515000,"text":"I will be seeing you several times over the next few days."},{"time":518000,"text":"I hope you're looking forward to that. Thank you very much."},{"time":521000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":523000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}